<div class="red bold">Example 4.2:</div>
Solve

<span class="l-example">
\( u^{\prime \prime \prime}(x)=6+x-\int_{0}^{1} x u^{\prime \prime}(t) d t ; u(0)=-1, u^{\prime}(0)=1, u^{\prime \prime}(0)=-2 \) by Modified ADM.
</div>

<br>
<div class="red bold">Solution 4.2:</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( \int u^{\prime \prime \prime}(x)=\int 6+x-\int_{0}^{1} x u^{\prime \prime}(t) d t \)
</div>


<div class="l-example">
\( u^{\prime \prime}(x)-\underset{-2}{u^{\prime \prime}(0)}=6 x+\frac{x^{2}}{2}-\frac{x^{2}}{2} \int_{0}^{1} u^{\prime \prime}(t) d t  \)
</div>


<div class="l-example">
\( \int u^{\prime \prime}(x)=\int 6 x+\frac{x^{2}}{2}-\frac{x^{2}}{2} \int_{0}^{1} u^{\prime \prime}(t) d t \)
</div>


<div class="l-example">
\( u^{\prime}(x)-\underset{1}{u^{\prime}(0)}=\frac{6 x^{2}}{2}+\frac{x^{3}}{6}-2 x-\frac{x^{3}}{6} \int_{0}^{1} u^{\prime \prime}(t) d t \)
</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( u^{\prime}(x)=3 x^{2}+\frac{x^{3}}{6}-2 x+1-\frac{x^{3}}{6} \int_{0}^{1} u^{\prime \prime}(t) d t \)
</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( u(x)-\underset{1}{u^{\prime}(x)}=x^{3}+\frac{x^{4}}{24}-x^{2}+x-\frac{x^{4}}{24} \int_{0}^{1} u^{\prime \prime}(t) d t \)
</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( u(x)=x^{3}+\frac{x^{4}}{24}-x^{2}+x-1-\frac{x^{4}}{24} \int_{0}^{1} u^{\prime \prime}(t) d t \)
</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( u_{0}(x)=\cancel{\frac{x^{4}}{24}}+x^{3}-x^{2}+x-1 \rightarrow u_{0}^{\prime \prime}(t)=6 t+\frac{t^{2}}{2}-2 \)
</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( u_{1}(x)=-\left.\frac{x^{4}}{24} \int_{0}^{1}\left(6 t+\frac{t^{2}}{2}-2\right) d t \Rightarrow \frac{x^{4}}{24}\left(\frac{6 t^{2}}{2}-2 t\right)\right|_{0} ^{1} \)
</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( u_{1}(x)=-\frac{x^{4}}{24}\left(3+\frac{1}{6}-2\right) \)
</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( u(x)=x^{3}-x^{2}+x-1 \)
</div>

<div class="l-example">
\( u_{1}(x)=-\frac{x^{4}}{24} . \frac{7}{6}=-\frac{x^{4}}{24}\left(1+\frac{1}{6}\right)=\underset{noise term}{-\frac{x^{4}}{24}}-\frac{x^{4}}{24} . \frac{1}{6} \)
</div>


